subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Lucie Safarova, a 19-year-old left-hander from the Czech Republic, stunned herself and second-seeded Amélie Mauresmo on Sunday by winning their fourth-round match, 6-4, 6-3.
